Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnNirmala UI\fs75\fscx125}य{\fsp-11.25} {\fsp0}न्{\fsp-14.25} {\fsp0}त्{\fsp-14.25} {\fsp0}र  स{\fsp-11.25} {\fsp0}र्{\fsp-14.25} {\fsp0}व{\fsp-11.25} {\fsp0}स्{\fsp-14.25} {\fsp0}व{\r}的封存区域确定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让克利斯她们立即赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要石已毁　你到底还有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想聆听你的歌声而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:44.38,IN_M_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fad(60,60)\blur3}Seilien coffin airget-lámh tron
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾身为剑　前路未开　岂可…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝若身即为剑　便拜服于吾哲学足下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑与吾千锤百炼之躯…乃至尊严…都在分崩离析…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,999)\fs52.5}<机械装置百科事典>
