Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯她们已抵达现场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为梦所伤　然吾仍将以吾心荣耀奋战不休…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾究竟软弱至何等田地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌唱吧　翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我既没能成为风鸣的道具　也没能成为剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要对胸怀梦想心存畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错　翼的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是被弃置了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便凌乱不堪　却是一尘不染
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是不愿失去与你的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才一直把房间维持原样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恶疏远自己女儿的父亲又怎会如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认清现实吧　你这笨蛋女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为让我能更接近梦想分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而故意让我远离风鸣家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若这是父亲心中所愿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以再一次心存梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就请您倾听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IGNITE模块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R}Dáinsleif{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我也来尝下鲜吧
