Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此等机会岂容放过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低调的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纵使你把出力提得再高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是定义为剑的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就必然是无法伤我分毫的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要对胸怀梦想心存畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾非剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能　哲学的獠牙怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尔称此为剑乎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此乃追逐梦想振翅之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尔之哲学岂可折吾羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阔别多日的圣遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这顺滑这酸爽真让人欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没搞错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然没搞错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃真实之子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔博士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支离破碎的东西已经无法再复原了
